What’s your pleasure in climbing? 
Chris says, If I can climb outdoors twice a week, I’m happy.

Seeking balance to maintain enjoyment. 

A new extraordinary YouTube video coming very soon with @chris_sharma :) 
🎥 @thibaudherrfilms #climb #boulder #escalada

Chris Sharma has been a #prAnaAthlete since 1995, and we’ve had the opportunity to grow together. Whether it’s putting up the hardest and most spectacular lines in the world, or hosting HBO’s The Climb, one of the things that’s remained steady for Chris is his love of discovering new routes. We’re excited for another year together!

¡Hola, escaladorxs y amantes de la adrenalina y la roca! Estamos super emocionados de anunciaros un BOMBAZO💣💥 y es que...el boss Chris Sharma está llegando al Roco!! El próximo 29 de febrero os espera...

🧗‍♂️ ¡Una noche épica de escalada y charla con el legendario Chris Sharma! 🧗‍♂️

Fecha: 29 feb
Hora: 20:30
Lugar: Sharma Climbing Madrid

¿Qué te espera?
🎥 Proyección exclusiva de “Sleeping Lion”: Sumérgete en la mente del boss mientras comparte su viaje y nos lleva a las alturas de su proyecto más ambicioso.
🗣️ Charla íntima con Chris
🖊️ Firma de posters: Llévate a casa un recuerdo único
❓ Sesión de preguntas y respuestas: ¡Tendrás la oportunidad de hacerle a Chris todas las preguntas que siempre has querido preguntarle!

¡OS ESPERAMOS! ¡Nos vemos en el Roco!

Building community is one of the most important parts of climbing and we’re lucky that @chris_sharma has been part of the prAna’s for almost thirty years. When we went to Rocktoberfest with him, he told us about the community he observed within the festival.

“It was great meeting so many climbers at the Rocktoberfest. It was a mix of seasoned veterans and people who were relatively new to climbing. All in all, it was a great vibe and so cool to connect with so many psyched climbers!”​

Read our full interview with Chris at the link in our bio.
